Another "mistake" has been made by the counterfeiters of the Hib Kft. from Nyíregyháza: This company was in disarray at the time (2001), when the group of the Fiatal Városért Egyesület was supposed to have eaten there - the mass administrator therefore stated that he had not issued the invoices himself.
Consciously Fake
